# Admin: full access
user admin
topic readwrite #

# Ingest: telemetry only
user ingest
topic readwrite zigbee2mqtt/#
topic readwrite application/+/device/+/event/#
topic readwrite gateway/+/event/#

# Control: commands only
user control
topic readwrite zigbee2mqtt/+/set
topic readwrite poc/commands/#
